{"hb4571cc0g269dg4cdcgbb44g5d47d58b71b9": ["A dragon's heart beats inside you. A dragon's blood heats your flesh.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "a5eced96-4b96-d1b5-fe89-ab14eba8ba0a"], "h64f56b7ag0e2cg49fega3cfg575a51564cd6": ["It is time I take what's mine.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "80610cb6-312a-3594-cfdd-d4524372657d"], "hb7244225gf374g49b3gbd7fg6594a24ace74": ["Close your eyes - <i>and submit.</i>", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "27acc90a-c6f2-21b4-2bf5-66062e1ced04"], "h2d84c70dg59d6g4332gb5c0gb339fa9345e7": ["<i>Close your eyes. You are hers.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "6c608bc5-5243-59c5-3b61-8e6d0bcd44e1"], "h22081e74gc7d1g49f1ga0efgfc96e3f7e939": ["*A pause. And then the flicker of a tongue across your neck.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "397489ef-3f1f-3257-c6f1-4526b86be4a0"], "haca21680g5cccg4344g9d0egfcba44ff7941": ["Open.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "7530e2ca-f8b2-a2d8-3146-783898c52bd0"], "h339e170fg5ea4g4439g901dgac30aba9e087": ["Taste.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "b191fe4f-b696-0e3a-c920-81dae29c917f"], "h348497dag2a47g4019g8e3dga04d1fbeba65": ["Enough. I want no more of this.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "ca4feca5-3170-90be-74f0-ecb224e43da9"], "h2258fc36g2de3g41c7g87a6g0b7e14adb6f2": ["<i>Do as she asks. Taste.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "4a0469f4-e743-1728-810c-5b90491ee8e3"], "hd2908571ga4e2g4a02g9f7egb828035c9930": ["Good. Lower.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "5a2c4132-977e-8f05-403d-e2abc9d77291"], "h3da8ca67g9a44g4e6agb2e1gc727774c5ca0": ["*You awake in pain. Your back, your hands, even your tongue ache.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "3c63fd42-8519-6edf-8cea-9f560214d6b4"], "h43ea40c1g8577g4113g89ffg751c10119d3e": ["It's time I return to my bunk.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "8ce3c4ed-aa8d-7d61-cca7-c85ac072928c"], "h4d816ea6gc161g4fd3g818fgfdb1479436db": ["Hold on - I need a moment to recover.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "45f7580f-ac66-be2f-0742-adac170f9c20"], "h0207f1c6ge446g44eeg9b2fg86ee6675a20f": ["Hmm - you do look peaked.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "08dae218-d828-9809-bfbf-de08f4f63ea6"], "h346e5377g017ag453agbd8bg588eec385eb4": ["Very well. Take your moment.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "aa60cb6e-b2d1-8fba-caa9-3c50fd20acd3"], "h6196dec8gda1ag437dga127gb8829bc697a1": ["Do you think we could make love again soon?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "bf21426f-c8f6-ac26-03eb-eb8bd243e9a9"], "h26500e71g09e1g444bg93b7g2cf3d1f279cf": ["Love? I might give you a lay, should my whims so take me.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "9abed229-31f9-0495-f473-864fb82f9f14"], "h42918d9ege10dg432bgac32gc1c512a3b11d": ["But I won't give you love.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "4f813599-603f-65fb-930f-bd42bf25737f"], "hbed2ae2bg036fg4b83g8cbag20ddf99dcf4a": ["Go to sleep. Our hunt resumes at sunup.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "3ab72c69-e236-dbd3-9d0b-45ed777b59cd"], "h5c715852g6846g43b4ga285gb70f353af3db": ["*Every breath, every blink proves exhausting. Perhaps the morning will bring relief.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "0a961abf-8393-419b-0995-e890227a36f8"], "h453fe3eege961g4c83gb6abg63eb22aead5e": ["What comes next for us?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "98824f53-331f-e13b-ec59-0e165af0591a"], "h4072a46dg53c6g4216g9039ge219c134667f": ["'Next?' We seek purification. I might even lay you again, should my whims so take me.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "c8805ec9-31d5-0b06-d21b-7c2a8f4ff7a2"], "h859cf602g8537g4943ga373g62f197e0feed": ["But do not deceive yourself: our bond runs no deeper.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "04dbae0b-2e96-d16a-ed01-ff75d0c53034"], "h30fdc3dbg0485g4719g81f1g7f9943132de4": ["Come back to bed. It's not morning yet.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "feb869ad-7dd0-5b92-c122-7655f2547dca"], "he0b8f0e8gd6e1g42b4ga0bcgf0c73c52475d": ["Time for pleasure has passed. I might take more later, should my whims so carry me.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "76c79883-6075-535f-0b79-c329eb86477a"], "hd3af4eceg78e8g4f17g8bcfg9d10775cd557": ["<i>Shake off the ache and return to sleep.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "5ec54514-efff-7c05-33dc-162252a4a3bb"], "hd06d81c6g7738g4776g95d5g02ded7bf590b": ["Tonight was wonderful. I really enjoyed myself.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "d898e45b-fcd7-3046-b90d-3ee43357cc9b"], "h33011e7ag43a0g4731gb27cg0f2ae0e532ff": ["I am sure you learned much from my mastery, Gith-child. Your training continues apace.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "61ba13a6-b561-1b94-598f-d1dc7c9e6515"], "h9d844aebgff9ag4d3bg9064g15529ab54ccd": ["You are a fit specimen. You might wield a silver sword of your own, should Vlaakith be so generous.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "bac295bc-bd4c-92b2-3d83-89ee942c9ef6"], "hcb0f55a2gf9d1g48d9g8f67g15cc2beb5352": ["Of course you did. I'm as extraordinary in bed as I am on the battlefield.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "50802ed1-948a-a9b0-ed46-07b3e772c21b"], "h637f05e8g1b58g4e0fg9909g013ad8d677e2": ["Do you think we could make love again soon?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "05e96a38-4f24-e3b6-9e2b-d8fc50d6a8af"], "hc216837egdfcdg4d1dg9d02ge3acd09a4b57": ["<i>Grimace at her arrogance</i>.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "cf77932a-1d99-55c0-7fee-ed1257da3ba4"], "h94ec95d9ga747g4b26g82d2ge96c3b501b70": ["Are you so offended by truth? You will find no better lay.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "be187dfe-6807-952d-11d4-cb4cf69e8a3c"], "h544812c4g2a51g4330ga20fg397e846427f8": ["Are you satisfied as well?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "e33a39da-83de-5b82-5eea-5498bfda2790"], "hb5fb5e01gfab6g4d37g969eg7358f670ba9d": ["My hunger is sated for now, yes.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "8d759c2a-10cd-f8e1-25b2-3b3845d1f734"], "h17c550fagc4ddg4a1cgac16gb613cd78da6b": ["I might even lay you again, should my whims so take me.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "c4963ab2-c2e2-33f0-fd71-c0dea93c9abe"], "h8497e0f3gd675g4852ga18fg2b83d8070b23": ["What comes next for us?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "1a8e2b93-da32-b063-72a4-87e34607fcca"], "h336aec88gd5fbg48edga387gb3217ff8af86": ["<i>Shake off the ache and go to sleep.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "0e8329c5-5134-c3bd-5c27-836f4ecc904e"], "h90cf173dg27f2g4414ga8b4g39401b68099e": ["Why in such a hurry? Relax, come rest.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "d70cf2fa-d2de-8c5d-3dd1-f011e08aa545"], "hc851f8e7g27fcg4a47g973dge610176c31a6": ["You made a fine partner. You will be an effective <i>kith'rak.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "7fbf07ed-ec0d-ee69-a1db-e54e1119aa99"], "h9fa107d3g827cg475dg925egebed2f531b86": ["Of course. I'm as extraordinary a lover as I am warrior.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "174d9790-7bb5-f2f3-f062-9e2a0f21de4a"], "haacd0b00g7f88g4b84g974bge7faa0dbdf04": ["You are a fit specimen yourself, kin. Fit enough to wield a silver sword of your own, should Vlaakith be so generous.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "36537d71-d96a-b8c5-9dcb-1121dabcf40d"], "h91245bf4gb88cg49d7gb36fg0f675c59bce1": ["Good night, then.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "cde40ec5-a073-66b1-bbf4-66efac74d883"], "h419e57d3g0b2fg4eb2g90e3g4131c42b8ac0": ["It's time to rise. Dawn is upon us.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "4964d2ab-0ba4-3fa2-976a-26f640df7c15"], "h65829b60g2210g46f1g9770g76df2ac494c9": ["Hold on. I need a moment to recover.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "5daf1566-6f85-322e-ab75-66b4078a1374"], "hb9c544cdg1f85g4916gbbd2gb81d1c2f0aeb": ["Do you think we could make love again soon?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "c6d738b3-a643-1890-5a4a-6cfbec8179fa"], "h8aeabd3cg9f45g42b6g8712g8794d040e01c": ["Up, now. Your moment's over.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "4ad52a8a-7805-7ce3-da04-dd50991e356b"], "h5230edcdg8d3fg4cabg88d2g7d3db400219a": ["*Every breath, every blink proves exhausting. A long day awaits you...*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "d3c6b5be-f7c5-9c3a-7eaf-d35278684301"], "hbf904029g8482g4d50g9df2gde0f6863577e": ["What comes next for us?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "d258342e-5716-5c60-6872-b57013173777"], "h9f9f8e9agda60g4f49gab67gc87e4c008155": ["Up, now. The sun soon rises.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "ced99db5-18c0-22dc-09f3-c742b07c9443"], "hc349b38fg782fg4de7gbaa5gc4c07792a103": ["Come back to bed. It's early yet.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "4b9aab2f-1d9e-74b9-73cc-fdb1ef55598a"], "h5828e164gf343g48a2gb22dg45fc70563980": ["<i>Shake off the ache and rise.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "6536afb9-2c8f-2290-3753-381e79e97969"], "hbb3293c3g3056g4f8fgb6dcg7a4e4fea595e": ["Last night was wonderful. I really enjoyed myself.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "5f38ea64-fbe3-f873-b9fd-310d7e291541"], "h964fa680gf228g4e92g9ba8g0415167fbfc5": ["Do you think we could make love again soon?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "cf3ab63e-ee1f-e521-e4e5-dc2b1006e1c9"], "hc5169fe9gd2d5g4c6dg89feg2bb6d1c096ad": ["<i>Grimace at her arrogance.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "211db6be-97c3-a751-5677-2abcc886a273"], "h7e66e683gbbd4g44bagb10eg42ed53b83d65": ["Are you satisfied as well?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "d29c5fc8-e34b-1b2e-6a32-0452ed67c540"], "hebab6207g50d4g461cg968cg3d5ecc73acfe": ["What comes next for us?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "0b4d1e75-a3ca-ea93-0c43-088976a1d191"], "h2cf5534dg8352g442bg8f5bg33dd4fe1cf3b": ["<i>Shake off the ache and rise.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "bb65e7e3-c86e-af9a-e19c-f064496fa580"], "h195e58cegc0acg4527g9ce3g2eef63be98cb": ["Why in such a hurry? Relax, come rest.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "870a4f55-d1c2-7420-21c7-b83c64ab19a9"], "h16ab84d9g0873g42ebgb8aaga9985758c399": ["You made a fine partner. You will be an effective <i>kith'rak.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "56fba889-57a6-9900-7d2a-7eab5fe11380"], "hc98de26cgd0a1g4787g9c3egafc10bc4dc22": ["Yes, of course. We will leave at first light.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "51ff2578-c609-965f-ef07-eef35c687c36"], "hccde1cc0gdeb5g490agab3ag75fd25722389": ["No. You submit to <i>me</i>. After, you can take whatever you desire.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "7f7ec5ba-a978-3360-da9d-f4f173d864df"], "h99a499f5g279fg4d8cga4c4gc41b7400da61": ["I am ready.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "dab13a53-02f6-9c9a-78c7-63962cb7e19f"], "h7e31ed75g3abdg46e3g8d93g9c0395f028fd": ["That isn't how it's going to go. <i>You</i> submit to <i>me.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "6352bc59-a1cb-68c3-5c5b-5bee0ef63ad7"], "hc19e9a54gc746g48c7gbb41g6f17fb1ffe94": ["You misunderstand. Allow me to be plain.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "7ffbfa02-52e5-afef-54cd-b7e804c714d4"], "h70a33e7egd467g4771g9e51g2c27e7720bfb": ["You are here for my pleasure.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "8c2f092c-efe2-25f8-5427-65a69c07bd70"], "hd7814cb9g7343g4a4eg96f6g65cf2b009ead": ["In my pleasure, you will have yours.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "f7eca517-cb4e-b381-45c3-5bd1f27ca60a"], "hefc7416cga014g48feg8dc5gaee7dcb02f4e": ["A final chance, then, to find bliss. Close your eyes. <i>Submit to me.</i>", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "59ee1d6d-967b-641e-276a-5fe7f380e571"], "h31bcca97gc3a4g4565g99e2g2f50fce91c39": ["Yes. I am yours.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "999af137-b56d-fdb2-403f-96227db85202"], "h417d3bf1g8a87g4896gaa6fg99867e7f392d": ["I've changed my mind.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "07b2bee9-24c7-55a6-6b43-90e815740034"], "hd9194d8bgb5f1g4cffg98b9gcd5676973764": ["Submit? What do you intend to do?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "10dda096-c228-0427-3566-605132f24191"], "ha0206eb8g7936g45aagbbe9gb6fd1914c126": ["I intend to take my pleasure. Say the word 'no', and you return to the celebration untasted.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "8af41a89-0870-4849-7a88-66aa7922cac3"], "hc9cf344cga045g4e43gbb39ge49403c198a3": ["Say 'yes', and you brave turbulent waters.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "0e52a971-0956-b5b8-6991-dbfd5556d46a"], "hc80497bfg2a82g4361g9eebgae3436c9ea70": ["Tell me.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "e2025e87-4d96-5aee-ab3d-2ff3e34fa38d"], "h48f706d5ga305g43cegb842gf64803b406fb": ["Yes. Take me.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "23759a9d-48bf-4b86-ad36-045118486e2e"], "h0fb5af0cg218eg474fgaeb2gc4d3dcc951dd": ["No. I've changed my mind.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "6a34c0c3-725e-6733-54f1-fea03297c051"], "h7fdf8001gbd94g42c9g8cfdg740e26e18ed1": ["You misunderstand. I will not submit to you, but <i>you</i> to <i>me.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "91e9fbdf-c35e-72d3-367d-fd984eca34bc"], "hd0b5bad8ga10fg4c53ga9a4g2a6c0bb9dc2a": ["You misunderstand. I will not submit to you, but <i>you</i> to <i>me.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "5351f32d-8aff-b13c-bba3-5a3be9cff8ff"], "h967e31edg4c9fg4282g9ba6gc309096c7df9": ["I've changed my mind.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "79065e85-836d-8c22-4123-214613214f77"], "h6e7cfe18g0aa6g4e41gb8fcga535c3ce6b7c": ["You would deny yourself further pleasure?", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "7ec65f8e-3e7c-5f1c-6216-fce9a2e82691"], "h4222a8e8ga15fg4864g8848gb0bc1ce70fbc": ["Have it your way. We depart come dawn, and no later.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "45749471-1dbe-70d3-6d00-3656b3d8be10"], "h8dc107dcg2202g44dcgb400g0071630e6ace": ["And you will take your rest alone.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "fc4d6d6e-15f6-a89c-646c-6d4b9e01d375"], "h5a80cc6egbcd7g4cf6g9383g941b34669edf": ["You are a child of Gith. You train relentlessly. You know your body inside and out.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "c7376ae1-3ae3-e8f1-b8b9-5e1467f2fe91"], "h67e9aaf9g1b62g4a88g938bgb0614240f17a": ["Gith train relentlessly. We know our bodies inside and out.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "c7376ae1-3ae3-e8f1-b8b9-5e1467f2fe91"], "h394fa166g5d6ag48e1gb895g15e6e8988c3a": ["It is time you knew mine.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "b5c6dff4-a972-7d9b-b896-80c8bcb50378"], "he95cec4eg872eg461aga431gc21572217a3a": ["Let me show you. Close your eyes - <i>and submit.</i>", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Sleep_Cutscenes\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SC_NightWithLaezel.html", "954841c7-b46f-9b4a-2770-bbaa708b4af7"]}